Anybody else?

00:18:12.000 --> 00:18:12.690
Yeah.

00:18:12.690 --> 00:18:14.683
AUDIENCE: Like,
population density.

00:18:14.683 --> 00:18:16.350
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE:
Population density.

00:18:16.350 --> 00:18:17.095
James, OK.

