We're pretty high, but we're
not the top two or three.

00:34:42.770 --> 00:34:47.070
But the world average,
my heavens, my heavens,

00:34:47.070 --> 00:34:48.929
less than a quarter--

00:34:48.929 --> 00:34:50.820
less than a quarter.

