01:01:49.870 --> 01:01:54.790
Domestic biomass
used in residences.

01:01:54.790 --> 01:01:59.420
All the oil is imported,
used to power motorbikes.

01:01:59.420 --> 01:01:59.920
Yeah.

01:01:59.920 --> 01:02:03.190
AUDIENCE: Do you
