01:02:24.116 --> 01:02:25.810
[INAUDIBLE].

01:02:25.810 --> 01:02:28.440
RICHARD SCHMALENSEE:
I'm not sure.

01:02:28.440 --> 01:02:31.950
There is some-- I'm
not sure what you mean.

